 add a touch of sophistication. Outside, the property boasts a private garden, a DSQ (domestic staff quarters), and two dedicated parking spots. The community enjoys 24\/7 security, a backup generator, a borehole, and beautifully landscaped common areas. Located just minutes from top international schools, shopping malls, and hospitals, Lavista Townhouse offers a perfect balance of privacy, comfort, and convenience in one of Nairobi\u2019s most prestigious neighborhoods.","agent_id":4,"facilities":["WiFi","Pool","Gym","Parking","Air Conditioning","Security","Pets"],"hero_image":"\/uploads\/properties\/691dd7c86f73b_1763563464-thumb.jpg","gallery":["\/uploads\/properties\/691db57cce0ab.jpg"],"tour_link":"","location":"Naivasha, Nakuru County","address":"Near Lake Naivasha Resort, Karagita","price":"36000000.00","currency":"KES","units":null,"verification_status":"pending","verification_date":null,"rating":"4.0","likes":0,"tags":[""],"floor_plan":null,"featured":0,"is_suspended":0,"sus_reason":null,"created_at":"2025-11-06 20:12:42","updated_at":"2026-01-16 10:53:52","is_deleted":0,"has_virtual_tour":0,"agent":"{\"id\":4,\"firstname\":\"Phil\",\"lastname\":\"Dunphy\",\"email\":\"dunphy@mail.com\",\"phone\":\"0791488881\",\"whatsapp\":\"0791488881\",\"earb_no\":null,\"is_verified\":false,\"image\":\"\/uploads\/1756456018_einstein.jpg\"}","reviews":"[{\"review_id\":4,\"user_id\":8,\"text\":\"The perfect work-and-relax spot. I stayed here for a month while on a remote work trip. The internet was strong enough for Zoom calls, and the ambience of the place made it easy to stay focused. After work, I\u2019d walk down to the beach or chill in the garden. One of the best stays I\u2019ve had in Kenya.\",\"likes\":1,\"created_at\":\"2025-11-19 09:14:57\",\"profile_image\":\"images\/pfp-default.png\"},{\"review_id\":9,\"user_id\":9,\"text\":\"Is this unit still available?\",\"likes\":0,\"created_at\":\"2025-11-27 13:58:45\",\"profile_image\":\"images\/pfp-default.png\"},{\"revie