including a large master bedroom with a walk-in closet and private balcony. High ceilings and large windows ensure plenty of natural light throughout the home, while top-tier finishes add a touch of sophistication. Outside, the property boasts a private garden, a DSQ (domestic staff quarters), and two dedicated parking spots. The community enjoys 24\/7 security, a backup generator, a borehole, and beautifully landscaped common areas. Located just minutes from top international schools, shopping malls, and hospitals, Lavista Townhouse offers a perfect balance of privacy, comfort, and convenience in one of Nairobi\u2019s most prestigious neighborhoods.","agent_id":1,"facilities":["WiFi","Pool","Gym","Parking","Air Conditioning","Security","Pets"],"hero_image":"\/uploads\/properties\/691df2ec09704_1763570412-thumb.jpg","gallery":["\/uploads\/properties\/691db57cea5c7.jpg"],"tour_link":"","location":"Upper Hill, Nairobi","address":"Near One Plaza, Ngong Avenue","price":"75000.00","currency":"KES","units":null,"verification_status":"pending","verification_date":null,"rating":"4.7","likes":0,"tags":null,"floor_plan":null,"featured":0,"is_suspended":0,"sus_reason":null,"created_at":"2025-11-06 20:20:45","updated_at":"2026-01-15 12:47:02","is_deleted":0,"has_virtual_tour":0,"agent":"{\"id\":1,\"firstname\":\"Peter\",\"lastname\":\"Parker\",\"email\":\"peterparker@mail.com\",\"phone\":\"0799678123\",\"whatsapp\":\"0799678321\",\"earb_no\":1234,\"is_verified\":true,\"image\":\"\/uploads\/1756462810_einstein.jpg\"}","reviews":"[]","images":[{"id":223,"category":"other","is_hero":true,"thumbnail_url":"\/loft-studio\/uploads\/properties\/691df2ec09704_1763570412-thumb.jpg","urls":{"thumb":"\/loft-studio\/uploads\/properties\/691df2ec09704_1763570412-thumb.jpg","md":"\/loft-studio\/uploads\/properties\/691df2ec09704_1763570412-md.jpg","lg":"\/loft-studio\/uploads\/properties\/691df2ec09704_1763570412-lg.jpg"}},{"id":224,"category":"other","is_hero":false,"thumbnail_url":"\/loft-s